    "description": "Note: This game is still in development, and content may change.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LAUNDRY is a Heisei retro-style 3D horror adventure.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2>In the 1990s, there was a laundromat in a certain town in Japan. This laundromat had been temporarily closed due to the disappearance of its previous owner, but it is now reopening. The protagonist, Hitomi, visits this laundromat and gradually gets involved in eerie events.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063400/extras/9fad554f916c02d0c66d509c36145e55.poster.avif?t=1747551355\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063400/extras/9fad554f916c02d0c66d509c36145e55.webm?t=1747551355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063400/extras/9fad554f916c02d0c66d509c36145e55.mp4?t=1747551355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game System</h2><strong>Fixed Camera + Tank Controls</strong><br>Players control Hitomi from a third-person perspective using a fixed camera with various angles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063400/extras/0fc8f3ea99b5912930c999622869d91a.poster.avif?t=1747551355\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063400/extras/0fc8f3ea99b5912930c999622869d91a.webm?t=1747551355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063400/extras/0fc8f3ea99b5912930c999622869d91a.mp4?t=1747551355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Hitomi's Daily Life Through the Laundromat</strong><br>Players guide Hitomi as she enters the laundromat and does her laundry. Through this routine, the background of the laundromat and Hitomi gradually becomes clear, transitioning the game from ordinary to extraordinary.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063400/extras/e6746cd7f6a35e706e3ad91ceaabce79.poster.avif?t=1747551355\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063400/extras/e6746cd7f6a35e706e3ad91ceaabce79.webm?t=1747551355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063400/extras/e6746cd7f6a35e706e3ad91ceaabce79.mp4?t=1747551355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Cassette Tapes and Portable Cassette Player</strong><br>By playing the cassette tapes obtained, players can transition into flashback scenes to learn about past events.<br>Each cassette contains unique music and audio, each with its own distinctive emotion.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063400/extras/cdd6b74067d842d0ab879e4aa223080a.poster.avif?t=1747551355\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063400/extras/cdd6b74067d842d0ab879e4aa223080a.webm?t=1747551355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063400/extras/cdd6b74067d842d0ab879e4aa223080a.mp4?t=1747551355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
